{"tid":2347702,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"梁朝偉激罕演出內地誇年騷　多位香港藝人參演大灣區音樂會迎牛年","createTime":"2020-12-31T08:51:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T19:27:42.000Z","uid":130626,"like":7,"dislike":239,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"eb868224032855d252b7fe03b2e12991c0d92d86","tid":2347702,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T08:51:27.000Z","msg":"明日便是2021年，不少香港藝人包括王祖藍、胡杏兒以及成龍等，今年都會出席內地電視台舉行的除夕倒數活動，就連一向甚少演出跨年騷的梁朝偉，今年亦會與老婆劉嘉玲一起出席東方衞視的跨年盛典，陪大家倒數迎接新的一年。<br />\n<br />\n另外，多位香港藝人亦已落實會參演央視主辦的農曆新年節目，送鼠迎牛年。這個以大灣區為主題的《揚帆遠航大灣區》音樂會，演出的香港藝人名單包括有容祖兒、張智霖、鍾鎮濤、鄭希怡、李克勤、劉愷威、杜德偉、呂良偉以及溫兆倫等。據悉，容祖兒會與周筆暢、Soler的Julio表演中港澳合唱大灣區主題曲《共同家園》、李克勤就唱他的經典金曲《紅日》。陳小春則會與內地歌手尹正合唱《友情歲月》、鍾鎮濤將會與溫兆倫等人合唱《萬里長城永不倒》。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201231/421312721053552640278054.jpeg/lbSyTD6dLY9RyWo4gFaLgJPTsCfzNEZkTQ6qgE0OqoA?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201231%2F421312721053552640278054.jpeg%2FlbSyTD6dLY9RyWo4gFaLgJPTsCfzNEZkTQ6qgE0OqoA%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=77eb406a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"64dc7f63ef122cfea38f493e21464315c3abea1f","tid":2347702,"uid":16808,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T08:52:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca96cb35250f5876de2e0cdaf0ab284882d28b92","tid":2347702,"uid":68261,"like":127,"dislike":1,"score":126,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T08:53:58.000Z","msg":"連佢都唔夠錢洗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dca0aff49f28fe47de1ab028b56ccea51c3d3da4","tid":2347702,"uid":66049,"like":1,"dislike":1,"